			======================================
				   Installing libav
			======================================

1. Requirements
	
	* Installed Anti-Virus Filter - avflt, please see the avflt INSTALL file

2. Download
	
	* Get the latest stable version at
	  http://www.redirfs.org/packages/libav-x.y.z.tar.gz

3. Compilation
	
	* Unpack package
		$ tar -xvzf libav-x.y.z.tar.gz

	* Change to the libav-x.y.z directory
		$ cd libav-x.y.z

	* Run make command
		$ make

4. Installation/Uninstallation

	* Change user to root
		$ su

	* Install libav 
		# make install

	* Uninstall libav
		# make uninstall

5. Problems & Bugs

	* RedirFS's bugzilla
	  http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
	
	* RedirFS's mailing lists
	  http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_maillists
